quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,65,"N’abeekika kya Aadi twabaatumamu muganda waabwe Huud, naagamba nti abange bantu bange musinze Katonda yekka, temulinaayo kirala kitali yye kisaana kusinzibwa, abaffe temutya"
  7,66,"Abakungu abo abaakaafuwala mu bantu be nebagamba nti mazima ffe tukulaba ng’oli mu bya butaliimu, era mazima ffe tukulaba, ng’omu ku balimba"
  7,67,"Naagamba nti bantu bange siri mu bya bwe wussa, wabula mazima ddala nze ndi Mubaka atumiddwa Mukama omulabirizi w’ebitonde"
  7,68,Mbatuusaako obubaka bwa Mukama omulabirizi wange nga nange gyemuli ndi mubuulirizi omwesimbu
  7,69,"Mwewuunya okuba nti obubaka bubajjidde okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe! Nga bukkira ku musajja ava mu mmwe, naaba nga abeekesa!. Era mwandibadde mujjukira bweyabafuula abasigire oluvanyuma lwa bantu ba Nuhu, n'abongera obugimu mu butonde, kale nno mujjukire ebigabwa bya Katonda kibasobozesa okutuuka ku buwanguzi"
  7,70,"Nebagamba nti, abaffe e kikuleese gye tuli lwa kusinza Katonda yekka! tuleke e byo ba jajja ffe bye baali basinza, bwe kiba bwe kityo tutuuseeko e kyo ky’otulagaanyisa, bwoba nga oli mu boogera amazima"
  7,71,"(Hudu) naagamba nti e bibonerezo n’obusungu bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe bibakakaseeko, muyinza mutya okumpakanya ku mannya gemwetuumira mmwe, ne bakadde ba mmwe, nga Katonda tabissangako bujulizi bwonna, kale nno mulindirire, mazima nze nindirira wamu na mmwe"
  7,72,"Netumuwonya n'abo abaali naye olw'okusaasira kwaffe, twaggyirawo ddala e mirandira gyabo abaalimbisa e bigambo byaffe, era tebabeerangako mu bakkiriza"